jamz.title: Spotify Journal Application
jamz.description: TuneCritic is a comprehensive music review application designed for music enthusiasts to discover, review, and share their favorite tunes. Whether you’re a casual listener or a hardcore audiophile, TuneCritic offers a platform to express your opinions on the latest tracks, albums, and artists. Additionally, users can log their daily listening habits to generate a personalized music collage at the end of each month, capturing a visual snapshot of their musical journey.

images.heading: /Images/jamz/page2.png
images.img-description: What fuels my passion for software engineering? It's the prospect of making a tangible difference in people's lives. Whether it's simplifying everyday tasks.
